807	        // TheoryLoader.hs:430).  Runs ONLY for `is_sapic` theories (exactly one
808	        // top-level `process:`); a no-op otherwise, so non-process theories are
809	        // byte-unchanged.  Injects the generated rules + `single_session`
810	        // restriction + `heuristic: p` into BOTH `parsed` (for rendering) and
811	        // `elaborated` (for solving / AC-variant pre-computation), so it MUST
812	        // run before `populate_rule_variants` below.  `user_set_heuristic` is
813	        // true iff a `heuristic:` item already populated `elaborated.heuristic`
