844	            // Accountability translation (HS `Acc.translate`, TheoryLoader.hs:430):
845	            // `Sapic.translate >=> Acc.translate`.  Expands each
846	            // `... accounts for` lemma into its verification-condition lemmas +
847	            // case-test predicates, injecting into BOTH `parsed` (rendering) and
